quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Bagambe nti, abange mmwe abatakkiriza (abawakanyi)"
  109,2,"Ssisinza ebyo bye musinza (amasanamu, lubaale, n'ebirala)"
  109,3,Wadde namwe temusinza oyo gwe nsinza (ali omu mu bwa Katonda bwe)
  109,4,Era siri waakusinza ebyo bye musinza
  109,5,Era nammwe temuli baakusinza oyo gwensinza
  109,6,"Mulina e nkola yammwe (ey'okusinza ba Katonda abangi, nange nnina enkola yange (ey'okusinza Katonda omu yekka)"